## ‚úÖ Beispiel: Guter SOP

```json
{
  "slug": "ai-client-proposal-generator",
  "title": "Client Proposal Generator",
  "is_sop": true,
  "workflow_type": "sequential",
  "estimated_minutes": 15,
  "time_saved_minutes": 90,
  "sop_details": {
    "target_role": "Freelancer, Agency, Consultant",
    "prerequisites": [
      "Client inquiry or project brief",
      "Your service offerings and pricing"
    ],
    "outcome_description": "A complete, professional proposal ready to send to the client.",
    "example_output": "[Vollst√§ndiges Beispiel-Proposal hier]"
  },
  "steps": [
    {
      "number": 1,
      "type": "checkpoint",
      "title": "Pre-Flight Check",
      "description": "Make sure you have all information needed",
      "duration_minutes": 2,
      "why": "Missing info = generic proposal = lost deal.",
      "items": [
        {"label": "I have the client's inquiry/brief", "required": true},
        {"label": "I know my pricing for this type of project", "required": true},
        {"label": "I have 15 minutes to complete this", "required": true}
      ],
      "blocking": true
    },
    {
      "number": 2,
      "type": "prompt",
      "title": "Generate Proposal",
      "description": "Create the complete proposal document",
      "duration_minutes": 10,
      "why": "One comprehensive prompt creates the full proposal.",
      "chat_instruction": "new_chat",
      "fields": [
        {"name": "client_company", "label": "Client/Company Name", "type": "text", "required": true},
        {"name": "client_industry", "label": "Client Industry", "type": "text", "required": true},
        {"name": "inquiry_text", "label": "Client's Inquiry/Brief", "type": "textarea", "required": true},
        {"name": "user_company", "label": "Your Company", "type": "text", "required": true},
        {"name": "user_services", "label": "Your Services", "type": "textarea", "required": true},
        {"name": "price_range", "label": "Price Range", "type": "text", "required": true},
        {"name": "timeline", "label": "Estimated Timeline", "type": "text", "required": true}
      ],
      "prompt_template": "Create a complete, professional client proposal.\n\n## Client Information\n- Company: {{client_company}}\n- Industry: {{client_industry}}\n- Their Request: {{inquiry_text}}\n\n## My Information\n- Company: {{user_company}}\n- Services: {{user_services}}\n- Price Range: {{price_range}}\n- Timeline: {{timeline}}\n\n## QUALITY REQUIREMENTS\nThe proposal MUST:\n1. Be ready to send AS-IS (no [INSERT] placeholders)\n2. Address the client's specific request/pain points\n3. Include clear scope, deliverables, timeline, and pricing\n4. Sound professional but not robotic\n5. Have a clear next step / call-to-action\n\n## Format\n# Proposal for {{client_company}}\n\n## Executive Summary\n[2-3 sentences: What we'll do and why we're the right fit]\n\n## Understanding Your Needs\n[Show we understood their request]\n\n## Proposed Solution\n[What we'll deliver]\n\n## Scope & Deliverables\n[Bullet list of concrete deliverables]\n\n## Timeline\n[Week-by-week or phase breakdown]\n\n## Investment\n[Pricing with what's included]\n\n## Why Us\n[2-3 reasons to choose us]\n\n## Next Steps\n[Clear CTA]\n\nWrite the complete proposal now.",
      "quality_checks": [
        "No placeholder text remaining",
        "Addresses client's specific needs",
        "Pricing is clear",
        "Has clear next steps"
      ]
    },
    {
      "number": 3,
      "type": "checkpoint",
      "title": "Final Review",
      "description": "Quick check before sending",
      "duration_minutes": 3,
      "why": "One typo or wrong number can cost you the deal.",
      "items": [
        {"label": "Client name is spelled correctly", "required": true},
        {"label": "Pricing is accurate", "required": true},
        {"label": "Timeline is realistic", "required": true},
        {"label": "No placeholder text remaining", "required": true},
        {"label": "I would send this as-is", "required": true}
      ],
      "blocking": true
    }
  ],
  "deliverables": [
    {"name": "Client Proposal", "format": "document", "step": 2}
  ],
  "suggested_next_actions": [
    "Export to PDF",
    "Send to client",
    "Set follow-up reminder for 3 days"
  ]
}
```

